 - 即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-giang-chu-th%E1%BB%A9/poem-nv76_bEgDF_AyZ3rSnDHQQ">Tương giang chu thứ - 湘江舟次</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/%E1%BB%A8c-gia-huynh/poem-K5-LgrqiwX_q8ooBmnAorw">Ức gia huynh - 憶家兄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-D%C6%B0/V%C5%A9-h%E1%BA%ADu-kh%C3%A1n-s%C6%A1n/poem-kHVi31E29_19w8t-5bzYeg">Vũ hậu khán sơn - 雨後看山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-D%C6%B0/author-D3wrKcf7SBsjhsqBdwn9aw">Phan Đức Dư</a>)<br></div>	</div>
